summary: This document is a lieutenant's daily activity log from the Metropolitan Correctional Center in New York, dated July 14, 2019. It appears to be a routine administrative record from the facility where Jeffrey Epstein was held, created shortly before his death.

events.title: Daily Correctional Facility Log Entry
events.description: Routine lieutenant's log entry documenting daily activities at the Metropolitan Correctional Center in New York.

keyFacts: The document is a daily activity log from the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) in New York dated July 14, 2019.
Jeffrey Epstein was incarcerated at MCC at this time, approximately two weeks before his death on July 23, 2019.
The log appears to be a routine administrative record from the correctional facility.
The document is marked as CONFIDENTIAL and is part of the Southern District of New York (SDNY) case files.
